sentences: During the 1974 invasion, he fought as a soldier against the Turkish invaders.
In 1975, he went to Athens in order to study in the philosophical school.
In 2004, Tokas and his six-member orchestra gave a concert in Vienna.
On 27 April 2008, Tokas died of cancer in Athens.

sentences: Marios Tokas (Greek: Μάριος Τόκας) (8 June 1954 – 27 April 2008) was a Cypriot composer of traditional music born in Limassol, Cyprus.
